name: Sun & Moon: 01/04 // Cityscapes
description: A sunny day in the city. Amidst all the hustle & bustle, the sun continues to provide light & warmth in an otherwise dark & cold, concrete jungle. On this day, the city of Sydney, Australia went into a 7 day lockdown from 12:00am, due to a Coronavirus outbreak. Piece 1 of 4 in my Sun & Moon series. Made on iPhone 8 Plus. 26/06/2021.
